query example:
select year,subject_id from link_respackage_student where student_id=21210301 order by id desc;
This query should be routed to slave node "slave_lessondb_0" node instead of master node "ms_lessones", but in the logs i got "2019-07-29 18:33:20.543 [pool-8-thread-1] INFO  ShardingSphere-SQL - Actual SQL: **ms_lessones** ::: select year,subject_id from link_respackage_student_1 where student_id=21210301 order by id desc"

@CalvinKirs  Just as @nancyzrh said, this PR only add a maven dependency for jmh, but does not add any test cases yet, so I think you need add test cases for that.

As my understanding, jmh only can print benchmark info to console which is not very make sense, we have already use jmeter to test benchmark.

The precondition for introduce jmh to ShardingSphere is we need to auto assert if benchmark is under threshold.

